<h2 style="color:red;"> Register your Vote</h2>
<p>
  Please vote on your proposal by first deleting the existing entry (most
   likely "Notvoted") then entering For, Against, Undecided or N/a ( for
   cases where a vote is not expected).  Please write just the one word exactly
    as written here in the space below.
</p>
<p>
  This is the best place for the proposer to vote, other members will be asked
   to do so elsewhere.
</p>
   <p>
    <%=f.label :"#{current_user.name}_vote".to_sym%>
    <%= f.text_field :"#{current_user.name}_vote".to_sym%>
  </p>
<p>
    <%= f.submit "Submit Proposal & Vote", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
</p>
<%end%>
